It's sad...you can solo from 1-40 with 2 10pp PSUs, but post-40 you really need something better- and there just isn't anything readily available in the h2h category. SMU will do for a while, but it would be nice to see some variety in the primary weapons beastlords use...we shouldn't all go PSU-SMU-epic-WLK-SHO. There's a little more variety in secondaries- a number of decent eitchatkas in particular- but we all seem to be using the same primaries because there really isn't much good stuff out there.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
